io.sphere.sdk.models

Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sphere.sdk.models.Base
      • io.sphere.sdk.models.Address

  • public class Address
extends Base
    Represents a postal address.

    Use AddressBuilder to create an address.

    You can alternatively create a copy of an address with changed values by using the with-methods:

    final Address addressWithContactData = address
        .withEmail("hello@commercetools.de")
        .withPhone("+49.89.99 82 996-0");

    See the test code.
